{"tid":2083492,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"急（突發）全民推行動post 香港人企番出黎","createTime":"2020-06-28T19:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T06:10:59.000Z","uid":342968,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"91f03366d391877317ac0d44de9b69e83e0c9723","tid":2083492,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:20:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">就快7月1日 香港人係時候歸位</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">面對國安極權法，無論連登定公海都需要重返2019年6月既公民質素。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解依加既運動越黎越退步？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">就係因為手足們由一個大群組，慢慢分裂成好多既細群組，一堆散沙點樣對抗極權？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁關提高公民質素咩事？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">連登變兒登係公認既事實，風氣敗壞到令好多人都唔會認真咁討論，而呢個風氣傳染埋tg group，試問冇大台又冇人討論，我地點樣發揮到200萬人既力量</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.如何進行有意義既討論</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">例如下圖咁，有意義既回應必須要有論點，有論點既討論先會有意義</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家最少要做到駁斥</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/29/022515_68d9cef242cfad976e20c86f95c8f181.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F29%2F022515_68d9cef242cfad976e20c86f95c8f181.jpeg&h=e0d92102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">eg.開花好定係陣地好</span><br />\nA:我覺得陣地好，<span style=\"color: violet;\">因為過去一年，手足對陣地戰既經驗比開花多，所以我覺得陣地比開花好。</span><br />\nB:陣地雖然多經驗，<span style=\"color: violet;\">但係開花既風險低回報高點都比陣地好，加上陣地戰武力唔對等，所以我覺得開花比陣地好      </span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後係要靠手足達成共識，再實戰實行</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n道理好簡單 但係呢半年連登而變廢登 <br />\n無論留言定係開post質素都係低劣<br />\n大部分手足既留言都係為屌而屌<br />\n要抗極權 要獨立 必先團結手足               </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">停止所有批鬥 <br />\n捉鬼 <br />\n玩膠 <br />\n偽黃論      </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">希望手足可以重整戰術post</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人創意係無限 俾我哋創造埋最後既奇蹟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>民族自強 香港獨立<br />\n今生只願榮光歸於香港</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6b59886168c93e0ae2256298e1ef4f4cba054ca0","tid":2083492,"uid":207327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:22:10.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"1799818088ff6a0111257a541de246871a6240ba","tid":2083492,"uid":19664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a886a9adfd6fcf8cca474ccb0dc240768cac8f91","tid":2083492,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:23:03.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"8decba2a4fe6b904b9e318b24c9d21dc444bd316","tid":2083492,"uid":342968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a886a9adfd6fcf8cca474ccb0dc240768cac8f91","tid":2083492,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:23:03.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n光復香港時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:23:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e19be307524d52cf7ef0ca89689d1da0be7ac73","tid":2083492,"uid":342968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:25:07.000Z","msg":"就快打仗 點解冇人傾點樣解決聚唔到人問題"},{"pid":"4ba69a833826159207ef34efba6303563a3a8fd9","tid":2083492,"uid":207327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T19:25:07